    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried calling them but they're closed for the weekend and i'm literally in tears from the pressure in my face. i don't want to go to the ER for a sinus thing, that seems like overkill. i checked online and some sites said pseudoephedrine is fine in the second trimester as long as you dont overdo it. i just need to get through the night so i can actually rest. is it really that dangerous for just one dose?",
